flavor_text_entries.gold:
It is actually
timid and easily
spooked. If at­ tacked, it flails
about to fend off
its attacker.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Because its fangs
are too heavy, it
always keeps its head tilted down.
However, its BITE
is powerful.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It can make most
any POKéMON run
away simply by opening its mouth
wide to reveal its
big fangs.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
GRANBULL has a particularly well-
developed lower jaw. The enormous fangs
are heavy, causing the POKéMON to tip its head back for balance.
Unless it is startled, it will not try to
bite indiscriminately.

their might.

flavor_text_entries.sun:
Its well-developed lower jaw and heavy fangs
are its weapons. As long as it’s not provoked,
it rarely bites.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
More timid than Snubbull, this Pokémon is doted
on by young people amused at the contrast
between its looks and its attitude.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
Although it’s popular with young people,
Granbull is timid and sensitive, so it’s totally
incompetent as a watchdog.
